Package org.fluentjdbc

Interface SingleRow<TYPE>

All Superinterfaces:
Iterable<TYPE>
All Known Implementing Classes:
SingleRow.Absent, SingleRow.Present
public interface SingleRow<TYPE> extends Iterable<TYPE>
An internal alternative to Optional, but when you try to access a SingleRow.Absent single row (equivalent of Optional.empty(), an exception specified at creation time is thrown. This allows for good exception messages like "More than one row returned for query ..."
